@Jean-Noel Can you briefly describe in what use cases you need this behaviour?
The thing is, that the GridDiv is perfectly usable for this, but the BorderImage does not support this. E.g. you leave the top-right edge emtpy. The BorderImage only shows the whole image and not parts of it. In this case you need to adjust the borderImage itself.
The main problem here is that we need an equal implementation for both GridDiv and BorderImage.
